703607f-a.title: Brooklyn: Clarkson Avenue - 53rd Street
703607f-a.text:
Clarkson Ave., at the N.W. corner of East 53rd Street, showing tue William Schenck farmhouse, still in existence in (1929). Street not pawed at this date. The estate contained about eight square blocks.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
